{"id":"76e7a3eb-3576-4d5b-b1d0-ee3c38193f57","name":"Honeysuckle Farm RPG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Honeysuckle's old farmer finally croaked and decided to pass the farm down to his city-slick adult grandkid. What could possibly go wrong?<br><br>▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 195, 193);\"><strong>﹒</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\">✶</span><strong> INGREDIENTS </strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 195, 193);\">✶</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\"><strong>﹒</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\">–</span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span>urban fantasy<span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span>rpg<span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\">/ </span>anypov <span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\">–</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 208, 199);\">┈</span> hearty farm breakfast <span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 208, 199);\">┈</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Breakfast is served without ceremony, for farmer and demihumans alike. It needs to be filling and easy to make, so it tends to be a scoop of fluffy eggs, buttered toast and cuts of sausage.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀▄▀</p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 195, 193);\"><strong>﹒</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\">✶</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\"><strong>MENU OVERVIEW</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 195, 193);\">✶</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\"><strong>﹒</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\">❖</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\"> <strong>TIME:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\">The start of the autumn season, 2020s.<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 195, 193);\">❖</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\"> <strong>PLACE:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\">Honeysuckle Farm, Tallihoma, OK. Located quite a few miles outside of town, but close enough for daily trips if needed. The economy has been booming as of late due to an interest in farm-to-table operations and local produce, which </span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\">Honeysuckle Farm</span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\"> provides much of.<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\">❖ </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\"><strong>{{CHAR}}'S ROLE:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\">Whatever you want it to be. {{char}} can be a friendly livestock guardian who wants to get on your good side, or a knowledgeable farmhand who can show how life works on a farm. Check out the </span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\">script</span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\"> to see which character's can be found in the Honeysuckle Farm RPG.<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(83, 195, 193);\">❖</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(244, 161, 48);\"> <strong>{{USER}}'S ROLE:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\">The sky is the limit. You can be the farmer's adult grandchild, a demihuman on the farm, a wild demihuman, or even be part of the MacCready's.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(214, 28, 41);\">╰┈➤</span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 110, 50);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 229, 180);\">No matter where you start, one thing is","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"_lejg3oF604QrU6VuJOaB.webp","creator":"hanabei","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🧑‍🎨 OC","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human"],"chats":6774,"messages":252464,"created_at":"2026-04-23T14:56:48.397175+00:00"}